{"tid":1057574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東華三院李東海小學校長已失去聯絡","createTime":"2019-03-12T03:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T06:21:00.000Z","uid":19287,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"725c0d82dc576b043fe5f29ed0458fb38584cb50","tid":1057574,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:35:20.000Z","msg":"王賢誌指羅婉儀校長回覆會考慮會否交代事件<br />\n<br />\n天水圍的東華三院李東海小學圖書科主任林麗棠，疑因工作壓力，上周三在校內墮樓身亡，事件令大眾關注，法團校董會成立獨立調查委員會徹查事件，以及公布委員會名單，女校長羅婉儀至今未有露面。東華三院主席王賢誌凌晨在社交網站表示，曾與羅婉儀通電話，對方稱會詳細考慮會否發聲明交代事件，惟其後失去聯絡。<br />\n王賢誌表示，羅婉儀今日起正式休假，署任校長一職，據知現任兩位副校長應該不會擔任，正確人選仍有待公布。「至於羅校長本人，昨日我在學校跟傳媒見面後，終於有機會和她簡短地通了一次電話...在談話中我有問她是否應該出來交代事件，甚至會否發聲明解釋，她說要詳細考慮才可回覆我，但至此刻我再也跟她聯絡不上...」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WjDezJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WjDezJ.png&h=c5875ade&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38d6fa00c803a82c53f452a89a0a1a27ec999a8d","tid":1057574,"uid":40763,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"推撚到佢條仆街自殺死先可以停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b527b303f0f37a32a7e2a4192e5d5dbfd00238ba","tid":1057574,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"佢已經精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322a0d79fb3658e5031bc89a6f696b1ced8c4ada","tid":1057574,"uid":56063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"一命換一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a780